			<title>Save &amp; Prosper Account</title>
			<link>http://www.gcb.com.gh/products-services/personal-banking/save-prosper-account</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.gcb.com.gh/products-services/personal-banking/save-prosper-account</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p>Save &amp; Prosper is a specially designed product for salaried workers who want to set aside part of their regular income as savings.</p>
<p>A fixed amount is saved by the customer on weekly, fortnightly or on monthly basis.</p>
<p><strong>Who Qualifies?</strong><br />Every salaried worker</p>
<p><strong>Your Benefits</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Secure funds for a rainy day</li>
<li>Earn more on your money with attractive interest rates</li>
<li>Withdrawals could be made from the account</li>
<li>Access to loan facility (should the need arise) after saving consistently for a minimum of six months</li>
<li>The repayment of the loan will not exceed your regular contribution</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Loan Accessibility</strong><br />You can apply for a loan, provided you have saved consistently for six months without any withdrawals. The loan amount will be determined by how much you have saved over the period.</p>
<p>After being granted loan, you have the flexibility of making withdrawals as you continue to repay the loan.</p>
<p>Your six months (or more) contributions can be used as a partial or total collateral depending on the loan amount granted.</p>
<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Two passport sized photographs</li>
<li>Original copy of any one of these (Passport/Driver's License/Birth Certificate/Social Security Number/ Voter ID Card)</li>
<li>A copy of any one of these (Utility Bill/ Tenancy Agreement/ Income Tax Certificate/ Reference Letter/ Employer's Ref, Letter/ Other Bank's statement)</li>
<li>Residential/ Postal addresses</li>
<li>Initial Deposit</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Other Savings Products</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Kudi Nkosuo</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>A convenient, secure and supporting savings product that enables you to develop your business or trade. Read More</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Flexsave</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>A flexible means of opening &amp; operating your savings account with any of the bank's networked branches. You may obtain a ReadyCash card for convenience access to your funds. Read More</p></div>]]></description>
