<p>Faster than going to the banking hall</p>
<p>Convenient access to cash (24/7/365)</p>
<p><strong>ReadyCash allows you to</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Withdraw cash up to GHÂ¢200.00 per day presently</li>
<li>Check your balance</li>
<li>Track your transactions using the mini statement option.</li>
<li>Change your PIN etc</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>How it operates?</strong><br />When you insert your valid ReadyCash card into the<br />machine, you follow the step by step instruction (indicated below) to have access to your account for any specified request. Please be prompt and cautious in the operation of the machine.</p>
<ul>
<li>Insert your card</li>
<li>Enter your PIN</li>
<li>Take your returned card</li>
<li>Collect your cash and/or slip</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Lost or Damaged Card</strong><br />The Bank must be notified as soon as your card is lost or damaged. Again, if there is a possibility of your PIN being known by someone else, you should either change it on the machine or inform the Bank immediately.</p></div>]]></description>
