			<title>Overdrafts &amp; Loans</title>
			<link>http://www.gcb.com.gh/products-services/personal-banking/overdrafts-loans</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.gcb.com.gh/products-services/personal-banking/overdrafts-loans</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p>Customers may need funds over and above what they currently have, either to expand their business or start one.</p>
<p>An overdraft facility may be provided in this instance. The following are options available to the customer:</p>
<p><strong>Overdraft Facility:</strong><br />This is a short-term facility offered to Sole Proprietors, Partnerships and Companies to boost working capital.<br />Features:</p>
<ul>
<li>Facility is for one year.</li>
<li>Interest is charged only on debit balance.</li>
<li>Flexible security arrangements.</li>
</ul>
<p>Benefits:</p>
<ul>
<li>Customers' cash flow needs are adequately provided.</li>
<li>Flexible terms of negotiation.</li>
<li>Prompt response to urgent needs.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Personal Credit Line:</strong></p>
<p>This is a personal overdraft facility targeted at high net worth individuals whose salaries are paid through their account at GCB.</p>
<p>Features:</p>
<ul>
<li>Income should be paid regularly into an account with the Bank.</li>
<li>Account should generally be conducted well.</li>
<li>The facility is for one year.</li>
<li>Loan can be repaid by monthly installments</li>
<li>Interest is charged only on debit balance.</li>
</ul>
<p>Benefits:</p>
<ul>
<li>You enjoy financial security.</li>
<li>No security is required.</li>
<li>Convenient and flexible.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Short Term Loan</strong></p>
<p>Monies advanced to customer over a specified period usually 12 months payable by monthly equal installments.</p>
<p><strong>Medium Term Loan</strong></p>
<p>The customer enjoys a facility from the Bank and this is paid back over a three to five year period with negotiable repayment terms.</p>
<p><strong>Personal Loans</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Target: Salaried Workers</li>
<li>Loan Period:- Consumer Loans are repayable in 6-36 months</li>
<li>Auto Loans are repayable in 36-60 months</li>
<li>Loan Amount - The Loan amount is 30% of the monthly salary multiplied by number of repayment months</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Repayment</strong>
<ul>
<li>Not more than 40% of monthly salary is deducted to service the loan.</li>
<li>Repayment of loan is on reducing balance basis.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 30px;">Benefits:<br />Convenient<br />Ability to acquire consumer durables<br />Payment of school fees, rent advance etc without hassle.<br />Ability to own a Car.<br />Consumer Credit Scheme (CCS):</p>
<p>This is a credit facility offered to salaried workers to acquire specified household items.</p>
<p>Features:</p>
<ul>
<li>Customer optains a Proforma invoice from any of our designated shops.</li>
<li>Bank prepares a Payment Order (Bank Draft) for customer to acquire specified item from the shop.</li>
<li>Repayment of loan is by monthly installments.</li>
<li>Benefits:</li>
<li>Eases financial burden.</li>
<li>Ensures comfort and well-being.</li>
<li>Ensures higher standard of living.</li>
<li>Repayment is convenient</li>
</ul>
